{"tid":1771241,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"全部同我入嚟，推到DSE搞唔成","createTime":"2019-12-05T17:33:48.000Z","updateTime":"2019-12-06T14:47:53.000Z","uid":262581,"like":13,"dislike":99,"uniUserReply":38,"replies":[{"pid":"f8072b37be0635bf32c06ed3560a68aae7aa2ce3","tid":1771241,"uid":262581,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":10,"replyTime":"2019-12-05T17:33:48.000Z","msg":"考DSE主科個幾日一定要全港開花，令到DSE考唔成，大學收唔到生，社會有一年冇畢業生🎓文革之中我地見到當大專教育停止對社會帶嚟嘅衝擊，更何況對一個開放嘅資本主義社會，只有更大<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n三罷搞唔成，所以要令中六同學全面罷考，衝擊整個教育系統，所造成對政府嘅脅逼唔會細過罷工<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />都咪話唔頭痕<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/shocking.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n我地要令個社會癱瘓，唔單止係交通，而係制度上嘅癱瘓<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />一日冇雙普選，一日社會都唔會正常。<br />\n<br />\n可能有人話阻人考大學會有人反對<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/donno.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />屌你咁同阻人翻工所以反對三罷嘅藍絲有咩分別？考到大學，好似而家咁，都冇Ocamp玩, 冇莊上，冇學翻啦。少少犧牲都做唔到學乜人講時代革命，同藍絲有咩分別？<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/ass.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"ab262b70f7bbc54e4b3bfc3ab3a11d286c2ecb12","tid":1771241,"uid":89514,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-12-05T17:34:50.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"a7a06982c13b441028caf62e2f298cff3f591627","tid":1771241,"uid":199670,"like":12,"dislike":6,"score":6,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2019-12-05T17:37:22.000Z","msg":"收皮啦 諗法單純"},{"pid":"137ac2e8f5757dbeb3aeec31d64995cda5fa3518","tid":1771241,"uid":262581,"like":0,"dislike":2,"score":-2,"quote":{"pid":"a7a06982c13b441028caf62e2f298cff3f591627","tid":1771241,"uid":199670,"like":12,"dislike":6,"score":6,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2019-12-05T17:37:22.000Z","msg":"收皮啦 諗法單純"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-12-05T17:38:22.000Z","msg":"點解？"},{"pid":"a59119aad810021d7c4211d6362d63c175edf521","tid":1771241,"uid":262581,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"f8072b37be0635bf32c06ed3560a68aae7aa2ce3","tid":1771241,"uid":262581,"like":0,"dislike"